              "value": "Smile and Wave"
            },
            "action_description": {
              "value": "Each creature of the guide's choice that is within 30 feet of the guide must succeed on a DC 11 Wisdom saving throw or be magically charmed by the guide for 1 hour.\n\nA charmed target must move on its turn toward the guide, trying to get within 5 feet of the guide. The target doesn't move into obviously dangerous ground, such as a fire or a pit. Whenever the charmed target takes damage, it can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success.\n\nA target that successfully saves is immune to any guide's Smile and Wave ability for the next 24 hours."
            },
